{"tid":971361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最後一架已當廢鐵送劏！中國比亞迪電動的士絕跡香港","createTime":"2019-01-06T14:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T00:45:39.000Z","uid":41404,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9d227086a91ce47bdd0936e660b0cd006e5e4e2e","tid":971361,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"6年前高調殺入香港市場的國產比亞迪電動的士，原來已悄悄撤出香港。最後一架比亞迪電動的士用家、西北區的士司機從業員總會主席黃永忠向《蘋果》證實，他於2016年購入的比亞迪「e6 400」型號電動的士，因2年保養期已過，換電成本高昂，加上轉做私家車需要繳付28.7萬元稅項難易手，2至3個月前已當「廢鐵」售予劏車場。<br />\n環保署2013年透過「綠色運輸試驗基金」，資助的士業界引入比亞迪電動的士來港，高峰期全港共有48部。黃永忠當時是首批車主，他指，第一批車營運期間出現多項問題，兩年試用期結束後便將電動的士轉售。但2016年比亞迪再通知，有新型號改良版電動的士，「成架車結構都大幅改良咗」，他見比亞迪誠意十足，便斥資約36萬元購入新款「e6 400」電動的士再試，兩年測試結論與上一代電動的士相同，都以失敗告終。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190106/59111399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59111399&d=Yn22%2BRciTYZw5tTnbpOTr7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3aff8b41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59111399&h=2976ee0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190106/59111399</a>"},{"pid":"6b71d403cd75435bcc365eb6c6a5c3ad017cdda1","tid":971361,"uid":45232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"已經好成功嫁喇<br />\n用左成2年都無爆炸"},{"pid":"c30eb2fac01f0692f2da72d0683d0c65aafc7bcb","tid":971361,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24075172b88f5c939386732dbf433a81b8d560a6","tid":971361,"uid":28309,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"不如直接捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <